headline: Ventas Q4 FFO Meet, Revenues Beat Estimates, Same-Store Cash NOI Rises
summary: VTR posts strong Q4 FFO results with higher FFO and revenues, fueled by gains in SHOP and OM&R offsetting a dip in triple-net results.

headline: Crown Castle price target lowered to $95 from $110 at JPMorgan
